DevOps & Engineering Principles

Infrastructure as code mindset

API-first design

Secure-by-default authentication

Observable systems (telemetry-driven)

Versioned APIs and backward compatibility

Getting Started (POC)

Clone the repository

Start services via Docker Compose

Launch the telemetry agent

Inspect telemetry via API endpoints

Validate integrations using Postman or curl

Detailed steps are provided in docs/onboarding.md.

